accessibility.text: The cover here follows a more modern style of comic books, as opposed to the more traditional halftone style. However, the style still follows the typical vivid colors and glossy hyperrealism. It swaps out the strong contours and halftone style for a more painted, hyperrealistic style, and sports a modern typeface instead of a traditional comic book style typeface.
